description:
Tom Bombadil! Barrow-wights! Nameless things, Ents, the Shire & more!  There's a LOT of things to go over in this one!  We'll go through all the references, theories, and story elements, while also pondering - did these from-the-book elements make a true impact?

Hit subscribe and the bell for great Tolkien content every week!
